title: Quickie: We're Going to LA
description:
KFC Radio heads west this week for one of the largest video game conferences in the world, E3. The only problem is that KFC and Feits know nothing about video games.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/kfcr
